race.comment: REECE UNLEASHED (4) took a tumble when crowded up close to the inside last time over 520m at Wentworth Park. Key player on best form and expected to bounce back. MAX SHIRAZ (8) hit the frame last time at this track but the start prior rocketed around 520m at this track in 29.48. Top win two back and rates a key player again. GO JO JO (3) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 8 length 6th at Wentworth Park (42.81). In the mix. MR. MOODIE (7) is a last-start placegetter in good time - solid claims again. Something for the Multiples: MR. MOODIE (7)
